name: Fruit Tree
description: A Joey Mars original painting.  A mixed media piece showcasing two characters in a surreal garden scene.  Crazy auras and floating clouds highlight these two old friends as they discuss politics, breakfast and the weather etc.  Oil, enamel, acrylic, collage on 16x20 inch canvas with a floating frame.

name: Avante Garden Cat Shroom Consciousness
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  A peculiar species of Cat Fungus illuminates the consciousness of time traveling soul.  Oil paint marker for the outlines, spray paint background and prisma-color pencils on acid free illustration board.  The image is 6x9 inches mounted in an 11x14 inch snap frame with glass.

name: Nice Surprise Box
description: I will fill up a flat rate Us Mail priority box (6''x8''x1.5'') with all kinds of Joey Mars merchandise and a couple of original drawings worth more than double the price.  Post cards, stickers, magnets, pins, keychains, incense and original drawings and more.  You will love opening up this surprise box.  Each box will be different and thrill to open and go through.  I will load these up with mega fun.  Trust me and I will thank you with style!

name: Street Cat with a View
description: An original Joey Mars piece.  A Cat looking to do a little recycling gets a view of a hovering UFO.  Oil paint marker for the outlines and trash can, Spray paint background with prisma-color pencils.  9x12 inches mounted in a 11x14 snap frame with glass.

name: Magnet 4 pack group 2
description: Joey Mars designs and characters on magnets... each magnet is about 2x3 inches.

name: Roswell Rabbit and the Ever Folding Dimension
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  Oil pent pen for the outlines, spray paint back ground and prisma color pencils on acid free illustration paper board.  A Rabbit has a funny feeling something might never be the same.  The image board is 9x12 inches.  The snap frame and glass the piece is mounted in is 11x14 inches.

name: Surreal Math and the Portal Grid
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  Oil pen, spray paint and prisma color pencils on acid free paper illustration board.  A Time traveler appears in a surreal landscape flanked by a grid containing a formula to open a portal to a new understanding.  Mounted and shipped in a snap frame with glass.  Image is 6x9 inches.  Snap frame is 11x14.

name: Brothers in Spirit Connected Through Time and Space
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  Oil pen on acid free illustration board.  Size is 9x12 inches.  A spirit world journey piece.

name: Evolution 3
description: Original painting by Joey Mars.  Ink, watercolor and gouache on 140 lb cold press paper 7''x5'' in a snap frame with glass.  A Hybrid Being stands guard on the dawn of a new awakening.  Geometric patterns and numbers illustrate the sequence code.  A metamorphosis symbol floats above the portal with pyramids in the background.

name: Today Was Different
description: Original work by Joey Mars.  Oil pen and enamel paint on acid free illustration board.  Around 6x10 inches.  A time traveler named Henry plugs in the formula to open up a new world of possibilities.

name: Breaking Open the Head
description: A one of a kind mixed media work by Joey Mars.  Collaged pop culture images, paint, pens on acid free card stock.  7x5 inches.  A mixture of collage and hand painted items. shipped with an acid free backing board in acid free mylar sleeve.

name: Eyeball cactus
description: An original painting by Joey Mars.  12''Wx9''H enamel and oil on masonite wood panel with a floating frame.  Is nature conscious?  Is it watching, listening?  Can we communicate with the plants?  The rabbit wants to know!

name: Green Monster Tourist Info
description: A one of a kind mixed media work by Joey Mars.  Collage, paint, pens on acid free card stock.  7x5 inches.  A mixture of collage and hand painted items. shipped with an acid free backing board in acid free mylar sleeve

name: Surf's UP... Roswell Stylie!
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  Got the surf board on the roof and the pedal to metal.  Hot Rods, UFO's and aliens...perfect summer day fun in the sun.  Oil paintmarker for the outlines, spray paint background with prima color pencils.  Image size is 6x9 inches mounted in a 11x14 snap frame with glass.

name: Stopped Time Encounter with a Green Cat
description: A 5''Wx7''H original painting by Joey Mars.  Oil and enamel on wood panel with a black frame

name: Outer Dimensions
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  Acrylic, enamel, oil and collage on canvas with a floating frame.  20''Wx16''H canvas size.  A multi layered painting created by cutting up various canvases (previously painted by myself) and collaging them together to make a new work, then painting on top of the assembled piece to bring it all together.  The theme of this work is a dream scape setting where there are various dreams going on at the same time.  Lots of textures and gorgeous colors in this work.

name: Recycling Hunt with the Blue Cat
description: A 5''x7'' original painting by Joey Mars.  Oil and enamel on canvas panel in a black snap frame.

name: Blue Cat Trashed Remix
description: An original painting by Joey Mars.  Oil and enamel on canvas board.  5''Wx7''H.  Smiling Cat checking out the recyclables.

name: Some One is at the Door
description: An original work by Joey Mars. Mixed Media on wood 12''W x 12''H. This piece has a campy horror movie theme. I start these mixed media pieces by laying down thick areas of acrylic paint and dropping in metal washers and some cut outs from books. Once dry I begin painting and working the surface with characters and shapes constantly trying to bring the piece together and balance out the color decisions. The final piece is a menagerie of characters, planets, stars, textures and plant life.

name: Double Jointed
description: An original work by Joey Mars. Mixed Media on wood 12''W x 12''H. A mysterious piece adrift with various skeletons and code sequences.  Different layers of information reveal a time traveler evolving from a metamorphosis. I start these mixed media pieces by laying down thick areas of acrylic paint and dropping in metal washers and some cut outs from books.   This piece has some canvas cut outs from previous paintings mixed in as well. Once dry I begin painting and working the surface with hand drawn characters and shapes constantly trying to bring the piece together and balance out the color decisions. The final piece is a menagerie of characters, planets, stars, textures and plant life.

name: Evolutionary Convergence
description: A Joey Mars original.  Let's see Charles Darwin figure this cross species plant out. Oil paint marker for the outlines, spray paint background with prisma color pencils on acid free illustration board.  Image is 9x12 inches and mounted in an 11x14 snap frame with glass.

name: Particle Sun
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  Acrylic, oil and enamel on canvas 18''W x 24''H.  Imagery, abstraction and data flow through the mind and sky of the Particle Sun.

name: Electric Sky Light Show
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  Crazy bolts of neon light up the sky as a UFO flys over the desert home of a funky fresh rabbit.  Oil paint marker for the outlines, spray paint background and prisma color pecils.  image size is 6x9 inches mounted in a 11x14 inch snap frame with glass.

name: Place in Nature
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  Acrylic, oil and enamel with collage on canvas.  24''Wx20''H with a floating frame.  A surreal garden scene.

name: Mediterranean Dispatches
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  This mixed media piece on wood is 24''w x 14.25''H.  Mixing in pieces of collage from books, metal washers from my work bench and graphic portraiture in a dream like dispatch from the islands.  Combining texts from Jean Paul Sartre and Tom Wolfe with a painted bold warrior face and skeletal medical illustrations and machine parts is quite different than a lot of my previous work.. I had wanted to use text directly torn from books for a while.  It all seemed to come together in a wild frenzy of a 2 day painting session in late December of 2012.

name: magnet 5 pack group 1
description: 5 graphic magnets by Joey Mars.  Each magnet is around 2''x3''

name: Magnet 4 pack group 3
description: Joey Mars characters and paintings reproduced on magnets.  4 magnets in this pack each about 2x3 inches

name: The Floating Head
description: Original painting by Joey Mars.  Ink, watercolor and gouache on cold press 140 lb paper 5''x7'' in snap frame with glass.  The all seeing Floating Head appears over the portal as the UFO hovers.  Intrigue and mystery abound as the coded sequence has initiated the God Head through the wormhole.

name: Encounter with a Green Cat
description: An original painting by Joey Mars.  Oil and enamel on canvas board.  5''Wx7''H.

name: Together Through Time
description: Original painting by Joey Mars.  Oil and enamel on canvas in a floating frame.  20''Wx16''H.  Transforming beings of math and myth.

name: Wamma-Jamma
description: An original painting by Joey Mars.  Oil and enamel on canvas in a floating frame.  Canvas size is 16''Wx12''H.  I refer to this style of painting as "Random River" where I am just free forming over the top of a spray painted background on canvas.  Lots of wild characters illustrated with multiple colors all letting the background color come through.  It's always an interesting balancing trip to get all these characters on one surface interacting yet having there own space.

name: Jimmy's Back From Iraq
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  16''Wx20''H with a floating frame.  Acrylic and oil with collage on canvas.  Jimmy's been pieced back together by the king's men and is back in the states.  Intense, a little cooked around the edges trying to figure it all out.

name: Dialogue at the Beginning of Consciousness
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  Acrylic, oil, enamel and collage on canvas with a floating frame.  24''Wx20''H.  A surreal look at the dawn of human consciousness.

name: Traveler's Doorway
description: An original work by Joey Mars.  Acrylic, oil and collage on canvas with a floating frame.  16''Wx8''H.  Three travelers have entered through a doorway.  Another waits just beyond.

name: Metamorphosis Lab Experiments
description: Original work by Joey Mars.  Acrylic, oil, enamel and collage on canvas.  17''Wx14''H.  Experimentation has begun.   The transformation is in progress.

name: Organic Computer
description: Original painting by Joey Mars.  Ink, watercolor and gouache on 140lb cold press paper 7''x5'' in snap frame with glass.  The rabbit looks on as the portal appears on the computer plant screen as the wormhole floats in the sky.

name: Shape Shifting Shaman
description: Original painting by Joey Mars.  Ink, watercolor and gouache on 140lb cold pres paper 7''x5'' in a snap frame with glass.  The Shaman enters a trance as the 3 sacred beings approach in his dream state.  The code has been activated and the wormhole appear as the attractor begins to migrate.

name: History as Metamorphosis
description: Original painting by Joey Mars.  Ink, watercolor and gouache on 140lb cold press paper 7''x5'' in snap frame with glass.  History as Metamorphosis is a quote from the late botanist, philosopher Terrence McKenna.  McKenna viewed time as an evolving, fractal like force playing out on the biological and metaphysical elements around us.

name: Sequence Code of a Floating Head Experience
description: Original painting by Joey Mars.  Ink watercolor and gouache on 140lb cold press paper 7''x5'' in a snap frame with glass.  This piece to me has the feel of an ancient text uncovered in a future past.  Symbols, numbers and geometric shapes point the way in this sacred text to uncovering the portal of a new world.  Can you piece the puzzle together as the search for enlightenment proceeds.

name: Metamorphosis of a Hybrid Shaman
description: Original painting by Joey Mars.  Ink, watercolor and gouache on 140lb cold press paper in a snap frame with glass.  The 3 sacred beings approach as the attractor shape shifts.  The three heads of the higher consciousness can symbolize past, present and future or the three sides of a coin.  The metamorphosis has begun, the code sequence has been activated.

name: Metamorphosis of a Hybrid Mind
description: Original painting by Joey Mars. Watercolor, ink and gouache on 140lb cold press paper.  7''wide x 5'' tall in snap frame with glass.  A Being is transformed and enlightened as the Sacred 3 approach with pyramids in the distance.  The sequence has been activated and is in motion as the metamorphosis symbols float above.
